[Copy dr sebelah] How to downpatch RE4make: - https://gyazo.com/d22af11c2469c49c9901319eafa2058c As you can see in this image, the red dot is the .exe (for WW_2 released 24/04/23) and the blue dot is the .pak's which are the updates. - To downpatch, copy the .exe and the latest .pak (so in this case 002.pak) and place them in a folder somewhere in case you want to go back to the later version. - Download the .exe's from here [Yang ada di atas linknya] Then, inside the games install folder delete re4.exe and the latest .pak (002 in this case) and replace the .exe with .exe from the patch before the current one (so in this case WW_1) and rename it to re4 - your install folder should now look like this https://gyazo.com/6384449fb6c08f691986420bb5c44fb3 and only have 000.pak and 001.pak (this is how to downpatch specifically to the patch before door clips were fixed)
